#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Visual Dictionary"
msgstr "Un diccionari visual"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:20
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &plasma-workspaces; feature many different graphical user interface "
"elements, commonly known as <quote>widgets</quote>. This guide will "
"introduce you to their names and functions."
msgstr ""
"Les característiques dels &plasma-workspaces; disposen de molts elements per "
"a la interfície gràfica d'usuari, comunament conegudes com a <quote>ginys</"
"quote>. Esta guia vos presentarà els seus els noms i funcions."

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:25
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Big Picture"
msgstr "El panorama global"

#. Tag: title
#: ui.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Windows"
msgstr "Finestres"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: ui.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Window"
msgstr "Una finestra"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the window of the &kwrite;, a text editor. Click on part of the "
"window to learn more about it."
msgstr ""
"Esta és la finestra de &kwrite;, un editor de text. Cliqueu damunt de la "
"part de la finestra per a aprendre'n més quant a ell."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid "The <emphasis role=\"bold\">Window Menu</emphasis>"
msgstr "El <emphasis role=\"bold\">menú Finestra</emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-titlebar\">Titlebar</"
"link></emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"La <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-titlebar\">barra de "
"títol</link></emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Buttons to <emphasis>minimize</emphasis>, <emphasis>maximize</emphasis>, or "
"<emphasis>close</emphasis> the window"
msgstr ""
"Botons per a <emphasis>minimitzar</emphasis>, <emphasis>maximitzar</"
"emphasis> o <emphasis>tancar</emphasis> la finestra"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-menubar\">Menubar</"
"link></emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"La <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-menubar\">barra de "
"menús</link></emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-toolbar\">Toolbar</"
"link></emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"La <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-toolbar\">barra "
"d'eines</link></emphasis>"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A very large <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-text-area"
"\">Text Area</link></emphasis> that acts as this program's <emphasis role="
"\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-central-widget\">Central Widget</link></"
"emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"Una <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-text-area\">àrea de "
"text</link></emphasis> molt gran que actua com a <emphasis role=\"bold"
"\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-central-widget\">giny central</link></"
"emphasis> d'este programa"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A vertical <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-scrollbar"
"\">Scrollbar</link></emphasis> (there is also a horizontal scrollbar below "
"the text box)"
msgstr ""
"Una <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-scrollbar\">barra de "
"desplaçament</link></emphasis> vertical (també hi ha una barra de "
"desplaçament horitzontal davall del quadro de text)"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-statusbar"
"\">Statusbar</link></emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"La <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-statusbar\">barra "
"d'estat</link></emphasis>"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: ui.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "Another Window"
msgstr "Una altra finestra"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the another window, that of the &dolphin; file manager. Click on "
"part of the window to learn more about it."
msgstr ""
"Esta és una altra finestra, la del gestor de fitxers &dolphin;. Cliqueu "
"damunt de la part de la finestra per a aprendre més sobre seu."

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-panel\">panel</link></"
"emphasis> that contains a list of Places on the computer system"
msgstr ""
"Un <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-panel\">quadro</link></"
"emphasis> que conté una llista dels Llocs en el sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-breadcrumb"
"\">Breadcrumb</link></emphasis> of the path of the displayed folder"
msgstr ""
"Una <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-breadcrumb\">àrea de "
"selecció</link></emphasis> del camí de la carpeta que es mostra"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A folder <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-icon\">Icon</"
"link></emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"Una <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-icon\">icona</link></"
"emphasis> de carpeta"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A file <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-icon\">Icon</"
"link></emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"Una <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-icon\">icona</link></"
"emphasis> de fitxer"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A highlighted <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-icon"
"\">Icon</link></emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"Una <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-icon\">icona</link></"
"emphasis> ressaltada"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-context-menu\">Context "
"Menu</link></emphasis> listing actions that can be performed on a file"
msgstr ""
"Un <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-context-menu\">menú "
"contextual</link></emphasis> que llista les accions que es poden realitzar "
"sobre un fitxer"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:151
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-slider\">Slider</link></"
"emphasis> that changes the size of the <link linkend=\"visualdict-icon"
"\">Icons</link> displayed"
msgstr ""
"Un <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-slider\">control "
"lliscant</link></emphasis> que canvia la mida de les <link linkend="
"\"visualdict-icon\">icones</link> mostrades"

#. Tag: para
#: ui.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-panel\">Panels</"
"link></emphasis>"
msgstr ""
"Més <emphasis role=\"bold\"><link linkend=\"visualdict-panel\">Quadros</"
"link></emphasis>"

